answers,'' but emphasized his long-expressed concern for the educational system and the need to bring the federal deficit into line. <PERSON> Kerrey </PERSON> lost one leg below the knee during a <ORGANIZATION> Navy </ORGANIZATION> SEAL team operation in the Vietnam War. He was awarded the Congressional Medal of Honor.
